<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, February 24 (Xinhua) -- Chairman of the Central
Committee of the Communist Party of Czech and Moravia, Miroslav
Grebenicek, has expressed condolences to the Chinese Communist
Party over the death of Deng Xiaoping.
</P>
