<BODY>
<HEADLINE> World Political Parties Condole on Deng's Death </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, February 24 (Xinhua) -- Leaders of various political
parties from around the world have sent condolences to the Chinese
Communist Party over the death of Deng Xiaoping.
</P>
<P>
They include:
</P>
<P>
The Peruvian Communist Party
</P>
<P>
The Bulgarian Socialist Party
</P>
<P>
Socialist Party of Peru
</P>
<P>
Head of Asia Association in France
