<HEADLINE> Cypriot Delegation Visits Iraq for Oil Purchase </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NICOSIA, February 25 (Xinhua) -- A Cypriot trade delegation is
visiting Iraq to discuss the possibility of purchasing Iraqi oil,
Cyprus news agency reported today.
</P>
<P>
The delegation, which is expected to return home late
tonight, includes representatives of the ministries of commerce,
industry and tourism, the Cyprus Petroleum Refinery and oil
companies.
