<HEADLINE> People's Daily Editorial Mourns Deng's Passing (3) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
We shall forever remember Comrade Deng's great theories. He
combined the basic principles of Marxism and Leninism with the
reality of the contemporary China, beginning the process of
reforms and opening up, and the socialist modernization drive,
under new historical conditions.
</P>
<P>
By summing up the experience, the successes, and the setbacks
in our country's socialist construction and learning from other
socialist countries' experience, he developed Mao Zedong Thought,
grasping the essence of socialism scientifically, and for the
first time, answering a series of questions in a systematic way
about how to consolidate and develop socialism in a country like
China with a relatively backward economy and culture, after the
proletariat seized state power.
</P>
<P>
Comrade Deng was a great theorist, and the theory he developed
was significant in the annals of the development of Marxism. All
the successes of our country in reforms and opening-up were
achieved under the guidance of his theory.
</P>
<P>
Practical experience has proved that the theory conforms to
the reality of the initial stage of socialism in our country, and
possesses great vitality. We must hold high the banner of this great
theory to achieve our goals for the next century.
</P>
<P>
Deng's theory on building socialism with Chinese
characteristics is the guiding principle for the Communist Party
of China, and the spiritual support for the Chinese nation and
Marxism in contemporary China.
</P>
</TEXT>
