<HEADLINE> People's Daily Editorial Mourns Deng's Passing (6) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Comrade Deng Xiaoping has parted from us, but his great
theories, ideals, and strength of character will forever
illuminate Chinese people's path of advancement. Under the
leadership of the Party Central Committee with Comrade Jiang Zemin
at the core, the Chinese people will unswervingly march forward
along the road of building socialism with Chinese characteristics
chartered by Comrade Deng Xiaoping.
</P>
<P>
At this moment, we feel all the more deeply the
broad-mindedness and great foresight of Comrade Deng Xiaoping as a
proletarian revolutionary. He created sufficient conditions for and
played a decisive role in the smooth transition from the second
generation of the central leading collective to the third, with
Comrade Jiang Zemin at the core, which helped maintain the
stability of the Party and the country.
</P>
<P>
Practice has proved that the Party Central Committee with
Comrade Jiang Zemin at the core has lived up to the people's great
trust and expectations, and is a loyal, reliable, enterprising,
and promising successor to the great cause of building socialism
with Chinese characteristics pioneered by Comrade Deng Xiaoping.
</P>
<P>
The Party Central Committee with Comrade Jiang Zemin at the
core has established Deng Xiaoping's theory of building socialism
with Chinese characteristics as the guideline for the entire
Party, and armed the whole Party and educated the cadres and the
people with this theory, thus providing a fundamental guarantee
for adhering to the Party's basic line for 100 years to
come.
</P>
