<HEADLINE> People's Daily Editorial Mourns Deng's Passing (7) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
In accordance with Comrade Deng Xiaoping's theories and Party's
basic line, the Party Central Committee with Comrade Jiang Zemin
at the core analyzed new situations, summed up fresh experience,
and put forth the basic principle of "seizing opportunities,
deepening reforms, opening wider to the outside world, promoting
development, and maintaining stability," which clearly pointed the
way for properly dealing with the relationship among reform,
development and stability, and for ensuring the country's
long-lasting stability and economic prosperity.
</P>
<P>
The Party Central Committee with Comrade Jiang Zemin at the
core, by firmly relying on the people and adhering to the Party's
basic line comprehensively, placed equal emphasis on promoting
both ethical and cultural progress and material progress, with
"both hands being strong," while taking economic construction as
the center. It has continuously overcome new difficulties, solved
new problems, and achieved new and important successes in economic
construction and social development. The country now enjoys
political stability, economic development, solidarity of all
ethnic groups, and social progress, and the people are happy.
</P>
<P>
When China scored brilliant successes during the Eighth
Five-Year Plan period (1991-1995), and reached, ahead of schedule,
the second-phase strategic goal set by Comrade Deng Xiaoping, the
Party Central Committee with Comrade Jiang Zemin at the core took
the opportunity to map out the Ninth Five-Year Plan and set the
long-term objectives to the year 2010, and is now making great
strides in leading the people of all ethnic groups across the
country toward the set objectives.
</P>
