<HEADLINE> Egyptian Parliament Speaker Mourns for Deng </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, February 25 (Xinhua) -- Egyptian People's Assembly
Speaker Ahmed Fathi Sorour sent his condolences over the death of
Chinese leader Deng Xiaoping.
</P>
