<HEADLINE> China to Carry Forward Deng's Behest: Jiang (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Jiang said: Comrade Deng Xiaoping was an outstanding leader
whose high prestige was recognized by the Party, the military, and
the people of all ethnic groups throughout China. He was a great
Marxist, a great proletarian revolutionary, statesman, military
strategist and diplomat, and a long tested communist fighter, the
chief architect of China's socialist reforms, opening-up, and
modernization drive, and the founder of the theory of building
socialism with Chinese characteristics.
</P>
<P>
Jiang pointed out: Comrade Deng Xiaoping's most precious legacy
to us is his theory of building socialism with Chinese
characteristics and the Party's basic line for the initial stage
of socialism which was formulated under the guidance of that
theory. The theory has scientifically grasped the essence of
socialism, and for the first time, provided a systematic and
initial answer to a series of basic questions such as how to build
socialism in an economically and culturally underdeveloped country
like China, and how to consolidate and develop socialism. It is
the crystallization of the collective wisdom of the whole Party
and people of the whole country, and constitutes the guiding
ideology of the Chinese Communist Party and the spiritual prop of
the Chinese nation.
</P>
<P>
Jiang said: Comrade Deng Xiaoping not only guided us with the
glorious revolutionary theory he established, but also inspired us
with his revolutionary style which was hammered in his long-time
revolutionary practice.
</P>
<P>
Jiang said: In the new march into the next century, to hold
higher the great banner of Deng Xiaoping's theory of building
socialism with Chinese characteristics and better carry out the
Party's basic line represents the unswerving determination and
faith of the leading collective of the Party Central Committee, as
well as the common understanding and aspiration of the whole
Party, the whole Army and people of all ethnic groups of the whole
country. We will more conscientiously arm ourselves with this
theory for a unity of understanding, be of one mind and one heart,
work with a creative spirit to open up new spheres, overcome all
difficulties in our road of advance, remove the interferences of
various erroneous tendencies, and adhere to the Party's basic line
in whatever circumstances.
</P>
<P>
Jiang said: Economic construction is the center of various
kinds of work of our Party and the whole country. We must act in
accordance with the teaching of Comrade Deng Xiaoping and grasp
this center firmly. All our work must be subordinate to and serve
this center. We must concentrate all our strength and wisdom, work
hard, build our country thriftily, shift economic development to
relying on scientific and technological progress and improving the
quality of laborers, and promote all-round social progress on the
basis of sustained, rapid and sound development of the national
economy.
</P>
</TEXT>
