<HEADLINE> Jiang's Speech at Deng's Memorial Meeting (19) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Communist Party of China (CPC) is the force at the core in
leading the building of the socialist cause with Chinese
characteristics. Comrade Deng Xiaoping always taught us that the
key to the success of our entire cause lies in the Party. We must
act in accordance with the teaching of Comrade Deng Xiaoping,
upholding and safeguarding the unity and unification of the Party,
more conscientiously rallying around the Party Central Committee,
constantly strengthening the Party's ideological and
organizational building and improving its style of work,
intensifying the anti-corruption struggle, and building our party
