National Congress, the Party Central Committee has held high the
great banner of Deng Xiaoping's theory of building socialism with
Chinese characteristics, led the whole Party, the whole army and
the people of various ethnic groups all over the country in
comprehensively implementing the Party's basic line, seizing the
opportunity, deepening the reform, opening wider to the rest of
