persisting in placing equal emphasis on material progress and
ethical and cultural progress while taking economic construction
as the center, achieved sustained, rapid and sound development of
the national economy and attained ahead of schedule the
second-phase strategic objective of "advancing in three phases"
set by Comrade Deng Xiaoping for us, and drawn up and started
implementing the 9th Five-Year Plan for national economic and
social development and the long-range objective for the year
2010. To greet the convocation of the Party's 15th National
Congress, we are now trying to make a success of our work in
various areas.
</P>
<P>
Comrade Deng Xiaoping has parted from us forever. But, his
name, deeds of merit, thoughts and outstanding qualities will go
down the annals of history and remain immortal in the hearts of
the people from generation to generation. Under the strong
leadership by the Party Central Committee, the whole Party, the
whole army and the people of various ethnic groups across the
