full of confidence, push forward the great cause of building
socialism with Chinese characteristics pioneered by Comrade Deng
Xiaoping and to build our country into a socialist and modernized
country which is strong, prosperous, democratic, and civilized.
</P>
<P>
Eternal glory to Comrade Deng Xiaoping!  
