<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Jiang's Speech at Deng's Memorial Meeting (17) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Chinese People's Liberation Army (PLA) is the pillar of the
state. Comrade Deng Xiaoping's military career held an important
position in his brilliant life. As the chairman of the Central
Military Commission, he charted the orientation and road for the
building of the army and national defense during the new
period. We must act in accordance with the teaching of Comrade
Deng Xiaoping, stepping up our efforts to build our army into a
revolutionary, regular and modernized one under the overall
situation of concentrating on economic construction, taking the
road of better-armed troops with Chinese characteristics, so that
our army will constantly make new contributions to safeguarding
the national sovereignty and security, and defending and
participating in socialist construction.
</P>
<P>
Making a success of both material progress and ethical and
cultural progress is imperative for the building of socialism with
Chinese characteristics. Comrade Deng Xiaoping repeatedly
emphasized that equal attention must be paid to the two kinds of
great progress, with neither aspect neglected, and that under the
condition of concentrating on economic construction, pursuing a
socialist market economy and opening up to the outside world, the
promotion of ethical and cultural progress should, in particular,
never be neglected. We must act in accordance with the teaching of
Comrade Deng Xiaoping, taking the "training of people with lofty
ideals, moral integrity, good education and the strong sense of
discipline" as our objective, striving to improve the ideological
and moral quality and the scientific and cultural quality of the
whole nation, constantly developing socialist ethical and cultural
progress which takes Marxism as its guidance, is based on our own
country and faces the whole world, and carries forward fine
traditions and reflects the requirements of the times as
well.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
