<HEADLINE> Mongolia Mourns Death of Deng Xiaoping </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ULAN BATOR, February 24(Xinhua) -- Overseas Chinese, Chinese
students and Chinese businessmen in Mongolia, and representatives
from Mongolia's non-governmental organizations, have gone to the
