<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Jiang's Speech at Deng's Memorial Meeting (7) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Under the leadership of Comrade Deng Xiaoping, the Third
Plenary Session of the 11th CPC Central Committee re-affirmed the
ideological line of emancipating the mind and seeking truth from
facts, affirmed shifting the focus of the work of the Party and
the State to economic construction, made the policy decision to
carry out reform and opening up, and then stressed in a clear-cut
way the necessity to adhere to the four Cardinal Principles. The
basic line of the Party, namely "one focus, two basic points",
began to take form.
</P>
<P>
The plenary session indicated a great turn in the history of
the Party and the nation since the founding of the People's
Republic, ushering in a new historical stage of reform and opening
up and concentrating on socialist modernization
construction. After the plenary session, Comrade Deng Xiaoping
became the core of the Party's second generation of central
collective leadership.
</P>
<P>
Comrade Deng Xiaoping guided our Party in summing up the
historical experience since the founding of the People's
Republic. With immense political and theoretical courage, he
insisted on a scientific appraisal of the historical role of
Comrade Mao Zedong and the scientific system of Mao Zedong
Thought, completely repudiating the erroneous practices and
theories of the "great cultural revolution" and at the same time
resolutely resisting the erroneous ideological trend of negating
Comrade Mao Zedong and Mao Zedong Thought. Developments in the
domestic situation and changes in the international situation have
again and again proved the boldness and foresightedness of this
significant policy decision.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> XIE19970225.0215 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1997-02-25 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Jiang's Speech at Deng's Memorial Meeting (8) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
An the 12th CPC National Congress, Comrade Deng Xiaoping put
forth the concept of "combining the universal truth of Marxism
with the actual conditions of our country, taking our own road,
and building socialism with Chinese characteristics". This is the
basic conclusion in summing up our long historical experiences,
and it serves as the basic motto which points to the direction of
our progress in the new historical era.
</P>
<P>
The 13th CPC National Congress, in accordance with Comrade Deng
Xiaoping's thoughts, systematically expounded the theory of the
initial stage of socialism, and gave a complete definition to the basic
line of the Party in the initial stage of socialism.
</P>
<P>
Comrade Deng Xiaoping guided us in formulating the development
strategy for the basic realization of modernization in three
steps, and affirming the comprehensive plan for reform and opening
up. He vigorously supported and promoted rural reform
characterized mainly by the contract responsibility system with
remuneration linked to the household, and warmly praised the rise
of rural enterprises.
</P>
<P>
He was the first to put forth the idea that the market economy
can be pushed under socialism, and promoted overall economic
restructuring with focus in the cities, creating for us a new road
of combining socialism with market economy to further liberate and
develop productivity.
</P>
</TEXT>
