<DATE_TIME> 1997-02-25 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Nicaragua Arrests Salvadoran Boats </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MANAGUA, February 24 (Xinhua) -- Nicaragua's navy arrested
eight Salvadoran fishing boats, with 22 fishermen aboard, who were
allegedly poaching in its territorial waters in the Gulf of
Fonseca, on the Pacific, the Nicaraguan military authorities said
today.
</P>
<P>
The fishermen, including one Honduran, were taken into custody,
and the boats were sent to the city of Chinandega, 132 kilometers
northwest of Managua.
</P>
<P>
In Chinandega, they were to be turned over to consular
authorities of their respective countries, said Lieutenant Oscar
Quintanilla, the chief of the naval force in that zone.
</P>
<P>
Nicaragua's navy has arrested 19 Honduran and Salvador fishing
boats so far this year for poaching in its waters in the gulf area.
</P>
<P>
The waters of the Gulf of Fonseca, shared by Nicaragua,
Honduras and El Salvador, are rich in fish.
</P>
<P>
The arrests occurred just a few days after Honduran and
Nicaraguan authorities agreed to install buoys to mark off the
maritime borders in the area. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> XIE19970225.0226 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1997-02-25 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Jiang's Speech at Deng's Memorial Meeting (13) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Comrade Deng Xiaoping not only guided us with the glorious
revolutionary theory he established, but also inspired us with his
revolutionary style which was hammered in his long-time
revolutionary practice. His lofty style and integrity were
embodied in his life-long activities of revolutionary practice, in
his experience of "three rises and three falls", and in his
efforts to boldly open up a new path for China's socialist
development.
</P>
<P>
When he was wrongfully treated and in an adverse situation, he
never lost hope. Instead, he was always fearless, selfless,
indomitable, dauntless and well-composed, showing absolute loyalty
to the Party and people, and cherishing optimism about the future
of our cause.
</P>
<P>
Invariably, the adverse situation allowed him to have deeper
pondering over the experiences, lessons and fundamental laws of
the Chinese revolution, which resulted in a strong determination
to accomplish more.
</P>
<P>
Because of that, he was able to meet the demand of history and
the times, and take on heavy responsibilities after going through
the adverse circumstances.
</P>
<P>
Particularly, his rise and fall during the "Cultural
Revolution" prompted his deep thinking on the question of "what is
socialism and how to build socialism," which enabled him to
resolutely lead the whole Party and people in opening up a new
path of building socialism with Chinese characteristics, after the
Third Plenary Session of the 11th Party Central Committee.
</P>
<P>
In the process of opening up the new path, he showed respect to
practice and with a keen sense, felt the pulse and opportunities
of the development of the times. While carrying on the
achievements of the predecessors, he broke with conventions, and
in studying the experience of the outside world, he never copied
the models of foreign countries. He always summed up new
experiences and created new methods by proceeding from the
realities of china and from the characteristics of the development
of the contemporary world. He respected the masses and was
constantly concerned with the interests and wishes of the broad
masses of the people, always taking the question of whether it
would be beneficial to developing socialist productive forces, to
enhancing the overall strength of the country, and to raising
people's living standard, as the starting-point and the end of
formulating policies, principles and lines of work. Far-sighted
and broad-minded, he always studied and handled the various major
issues in view of the overall interests. He advocated actions and
was resolute in taking actions, and in particular, demonstrated
extraordinary courage and wisdom in making important decisions at
critical moments. His style along with his cause and thought, will
always live in our hearts.
</P>
<P>
The passing of Comrade Deng Xiaoping is a loss beyond measure
to our Party, our army and the people of all ethic groups of our
country. The Party Central Committee called on the whole Party,
the whole army, the people of all ethic groups of the whole
country to turn grief into strength, carry on the will of Comrade
Deng Xiaoping, and express our mourning by working harder and
doing well in all aspects of practical work.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> XIE19970225.0227 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1997-02-25 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Belarus to Remain Neutral: Defense Minister </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MOSCOW, February 24 (Xinhua) -- Belarus will continue to pursue
a defense policy of neutrality, but remains opposed to the
eastward expansion plans of the North Atlantic Treaty Organization
(NATO), Defense Minister Alexander Chumakov said today.
</P>
<P>
Chumakov told reporters that Belarus has not listed any country
as its enemy so far, but it considers NATO's plans to admit
eastern European countries as a threat, the Interfax news agency
reported today.
</P>
<P>
Chumakov also listed international terrorism, separatism and
regional conflicts as other dangers, Interfax said.
</P>
<P>
Real threats from military conflicts are diminishing and the
nuclear confrontation no long exists now, Chumakov said. But it's
still too early to say the world has become peaceful, he added.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> XIE19970225.0228 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1997-02-25 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Jiang's Speech at Deng's Memorial Meeting (15) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Economic construction is the center of various kinds of work of
our Party and the whole country. The decision to take economic
construction as the center represents the most fundamental
achievement made under Comrade Deng Xiaoping's leadership in the
effort to bring order out of chaos. We must act in accordance with
the teaching of Comrade Deng Xiaoping and grasp this center
firmly. All our work must be subordinate to and serve this
center. Development is the most essential criterion. The key to
seizing the opportunity and developing ourselves lies in expanding
the economy. We must concentrate all our strength and wisdom, work
hard, build our country thriftily, shift economic development to
relying on scientific and technological progress and improving the
quality of laborers, and promote all-round social progress on the
basis of sustained, rapid and sound development of the national
economy.
</P>
<P>
Reform is the inevitable road through which China will be able
to achieve socialist modernization. Comrade Deng Xiaoping drew up
a master plan for our all-round reforms. We must act in
accordance with the teaching of Comrade Deng Xiaoping, taking
the deepening of the reform as the key to eliminating barriers to
the development of productive forces and further advancing our
entire cause. The establishment of a socialist market economic
structure on the basis of taking the socialist public ownership as
the mainstay and the common development of multi-economic sectors
is a great pioneering work that our predecessors have never
undertaken. On the basis of the achievements which we have already
scored, we must carry on the reform of the economic structure in
depth. To meet the needs in this regard, we must persist in the
restructuring in political and other fields.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> XIE19970225.0229 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1997-02-25 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Jiang's Speech at Deng's Memorial Meeting (14) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The theory of building socialism with Chinese characteristics
established by Comrade Deng Xiaoping and the Party's basic line
formulated under the guidance of this theory are the guide for
action which we must adhere to. In the new march into the next
century, it represents the unswerving determination and faith of
the leading collective of the Party Central Committee, as well as
the common understanding and aspiration of the whole Party, the
whole Army and people of all ethnic groups of the whole country,
to hold higher the great banner of Deng Xiaoping's theory of
building socialism with Chinese characteristics and better carry
out the Party's basic line. We will more conscientiously arm
ourselves with this theory for a unity of understanding, be of
one mind and one heart, work with a creative spirit to open up new
spheres, overcome all difficulties in our road of advance, remove
the interferences of various erroneous tendencies, and adhere to
the Party's basic line in whatever circumstances.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> XIE19970225.0230 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1997-02-25 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Jiang's Speech at Deng's Memorial Meeting (16) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Opening up to the outside world is an essential condition for
China to achieve its socialist modernization. Comrade Deng
Xiaoping emphasized repeatedly that the current world is an open
one, that China's development is inseparable from the world and
that it is imperative to pursue the policy of opening up to the
outside world on the basis of persisting in self-reliance. We must
act in accordance with the teaching of Comrade Deng Xiaoping,
soberly assess the development of the world, courageously meet the
severe challenge, adhere to the fundamental national policy of
opening up, develop an all-directional and multi-layer pattern of
opening up, strive to enhance the level of our opening up,
extensively absorb and draw on all results of advanced
civilization created by all countries in the world including
developed capitalist countries, and actively participate in
international economic and technological cooperation and
competition.
</P>
<P>
The state power of the people's democratic dictatorship
constitutes the political guarantee for the healthy development of
our cause. Comrade Deng Xiaoping always paid close attention to
the consolidation and development of the people's political
power. We must act in accordance with the teaching of Comrade Deng
Xiaoping, upholding the leadership by the working class,
consolidating the worker-peasant alliance, developing the broadest
possible united patriotic front with various non-Communist parties
participating, strengthening the great unity among the people of
various ethnic groups throughout the country, carrying forward
socialist democracy, perfecting the socialist legal system,
managing state affairs according to law, constantly improving the
political situation marked by stability, unity and liveliness.
</P>
</TEXT>
