a special unit of the Tunisian army during his visit.
</P>
<P>
Tunisian President Ben Ali will pay a state visit to France in
the coming weeks, which is aimed at strengthening relations with
France.
</P>
<P>
Tunisia neighbors Algeria, which has close ties with France but
has seen its relations with Paris strained from time to time out
of differences over the political situation in Algeria, which is
marked by a six-year conflict between its government and Islamic
fundamentalists. 
</P>
