<HEADLINE> Ethiopian Trade Mission Leaves for Tunisia </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ADDIS ABABA, February 24 (Xinhua) -- A 15-man Ethiopian trade
mission left here today for Tunisia for a week-long visit to
tap opputunities for sales of Ethiopian goods to the north
African country.
</P>
