<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, February 24 (Xinhua) -- People from the media circles
in the capital held a forum today to mourn the death of Deng
Xiaoping and recall his outstanding merits.
</P>
<P>
Deng died of illness last Wednesday at the age of 93.
</P>
<P>
The participants vowed to better study and publicize Deng's
theory of building socialism with Chinese characteristics and help
maintain the country's stability through the correct guidance of
public opinion.
