<TEXT>
<P>
DAR ES SALAAM, February 24 (Xinhua) -- President Benjamin
Mkapa will leave tomorrow for Gaborone, Botswana to attend a
round Table conference of heads of state and government of the
African Commonwealth countries on democracy in Africa.
</P>
<P>
