worst anti-democratic abuses and allow the more mature
democracies to lead by example.
</P>
<P>
Nigeria, whose Commonwealth membership was suspended in 1995
and the only country with a non-elected head of government, was
not invited.
</P>
<P>
President Mkapa is expected to return home on Thursday, the
statement said. 
